text: Junagarh or Junagadh may refer to the following places in India : * Junagadh, a town in Junagadh district, Gujarat * Junagadh State, a former princely salute state with seat in the above town * Junagadh district, a district of Gujarat * Junagarh Fort, a fort in Bikaner, Rajasthan * Junagarh, Kalahandi, a town in Kalahandi district, Odisha * Junagarh (Odisha Vidhan Sabha constituency), an Assembly constituency, Odisha
title: Junagarh
